{"tid":2509139,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警隊再推新招「行咇易」app掃蕩黃屍。黃屍：比條生路！！","createTime":"2021-04-29T08:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T09:06:52.000Z","uid":219635,"like":7,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ce619972e16ed859254de083c2d5fcfef70fff80","tid":2509139,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方下周三起，試用手機應用程式截查市民時讀取身份證資料，不用口頭上報調配中心，以縮短時間及減少人為出錯。警方強調，有措施保障資料安全及避免警員濫用。<br />\n<br />\n警員使用這個應用程式，先用手機鏡頭對準身份證，採取光學字符辨識技術，自動讀取證件上資料，包括姓名、性別、出生日期、證件號碼等資料，上傳到警方的資料庫核對，會知道被查的人是否通緝或失蹤人士等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"> 以往在示威現場，防暴警員會大規模截查市民，警方說日後會視乎環境以及訊號接收等，決定是否用「行咇易」，但市民不能自行選擇。   </span><br />\n<br />\n警員下班後，會好像警員記事簿一樣保管該部手機，非當值期間，應用程式便會鎖上，如果遺失手機，系統可以遙距清除手機上的所有資料。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁咪放工得閒都起人底？<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=432855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432855&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwdTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=e12f7c20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432855&h=173c6e34\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=432855</a>"},{"pid":"ce1e98e356b5b8a70498a06be2306b2da47c3f47","tid":2509139,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c776b74b6babf042c394451f576234e1c16006","tid":2509139,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"法治已死！公義淪亡！無天理<img src=\"/assets